111        1/1                if ((PL_ADDR_i[31:12] == 20'b0))
112        1/1                  broadcast = PL_ENA_i;
                        MISSING_ELSE

117                        assign preload    = PROTECT_i ? 1'b0 : (my_id & PL_ENA_i & PL_WEN_i)  | ( PL_ENA_i & PL_REN_i & (~broadcast | my_id));   
118                        assign smux_clk_a =  CLK_A_i; // preload ? PL_CLK : CLK_A;   //Preload only on Port A
119                        assign smux_clk_b =  CLK_B_i;  //FMODE_i ? (SYNC_FIFO_i ? CLK_A_i : CLK_B_i) : CLK_B_i;  // Preload deactivates Port B 
120                        assign real_fmode = preload ? 1'b0     : FMODE_i;
121                     
122                        assign ram_ren_a      = preload ? PL_REN_i : FMODE_i ? 0 :REN_A_i ;
123                        assign ram_wen_a      = preload ? PL_WEN_i   : (WEN_A_i); 
124                     
125                        assign ram_ren_b      = preload ? 1'b0  : ( real_fmode ? ren_o : REN_B_i);
126                        assign ram_wen_b      = preload ? 1'b0 : FMODE_i ? 1'b0 : WEN_B_i;
127                     
128                        assign cen_b = (ram_ren_b | ram_wen_b);
129                        assign cen_a = (ram_ren_a | ram_wen_a);

135                        assign ram_waddr_b = preload ? 4'b0 : real_fmode ? {ff_raddr[0],3'b000} : ADDR_B_i[3:0];
136                        assign ram_waddr_a = preload ? 4'b0 : real_fmode ? {ff_waddr[0],3'b000} : ADDR_A_i[3:0];   
137                        
138                        assign ram_addr_b = preload ? {PL_ADDR_i[9:0],4'h0} : 
139                     		       (real_fmode ? {ff_raddr[10:0],3'h0} : {ADDR_B_i[13:4],addr_b_d[3:0]});
140                        assign ram_addr_a = preload ? {PL_ADDR_i[9:0],4'h0} : 
141                     		       (real_fmode ? {ff_waddr[10:0],3'h0} : {ADDR_A_i[13:4], addr_a_d[3:0]});
142                     
143                        always_ff @ (posedge CLK_A_i or negedge RESET_ni) begin
144        1/1                if (RESET_ni == 1'b0)
145        1/1          	addr_a_d[3:0] <= 4'h0;
146                           else
147        1/1          	addr_a_d[3:0] <= ADDR_A_i[3:0];
148                        end
149                        always_ff @ (posedge CLK_B_i or negedge RESET_ni) begin
150        1/1                if (RESET_ni == 1'b0)
151        1/1          	addr_b_d[3:0] <= 4'h0;
152                           else
153        0/1     ==>  	addr_b_d[3:0] <= ADDR_B_i[3:0];
154                        end

156                        assign cen_a_n = ~cen_a;
157                        assign ram_wen_a_n = ~ram_wen_a;
158                        assign cen_b_n = ~cen_b;
159                        assign ram_wen_b_n = ~ram_wen_b;

164                     assign  ram_rdata_b = SCAN_MODE_i ? aligned_wdata_b&~{ram_addr_b[13:4],cen_b_n,ram_wen_b_n,6'b0}+wmsk_b : ram_rdata_b_int;
